title: Meeting Notes Organizer
body:
Organize these meeting notes into a clear structure:

**Meeting:** [MEETING TITLE]
**Date:** [DATE]
**Attendees:** [NAMES]

**Key Decisions:**
- [List decisions made]

**Action Items:**
- [Person] - [Task] - [Deadline]

**Follow-up Items:**
- [Items to discuss next time]

**Notes:**
[Raw notes go here]
